package org.apache.phoenix.iterate;

import java.sql.SQLException;
import java.util.List;

/**
 * 
 * Abstract base class for ResultIterator implementations that
 * do nothing on close and have no explain plan steps
 *
 * 
 * @since 1.2
 */
<fim_suffix>public abstract class BaseResultIterator implements ResultIterator {
    
    @Override
    public void close() throws SQLException {
    }

    @Override
    public void explain(List<String> planSteps) {
    }

}<fim_middle>// class below has no smell
